  "title": "Private Home Nurse",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Oversee and coordinate the well-being management of key stakeholders.</li>\n  <li>Deliver personalized, patient-centered care, including regular monitoring of glucose and blood pressure, as well as guidance on lifestyle and dietary choices.</li>\n  <li>Provide medical and physical care to key stakeholders during travel.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum of 10 years of proven nursing experience; experience as a Paramedic is a plus.</li>\n  <li>Strong medical knowledge, particularly in emergency care and cardiology.</li>\n  <li>Demonstrated proficiency in both core nursing skills and specialized techniques.</li>\n  <li>Exhibits a caring and positive demeanor.</li>\n  <li>Holds at least a Diploma or Degree in Nursing.</li>\n  <li>Willingness to travel overseas on an ad-hoc basis as needed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Additional Info:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Attentive and not calculative will be advantage.</li>\n  <li>1 on 1 support</li>\n  <li>Staff Benefits complianced with MOM</li>\n  <li>Advantage to have healthscreening, BCLS and emergency handle knowledge.</li>\n  <li>willing to travel when required.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd </p>\n<p>EA License No. 20C0270</p>\n<p><br></p>",
